---
import '../styles/global.css';

interface Props {
  title: string;
  description: string;
  ogType?: 'website' | 'article';
}

const { title, description, ogType = 'website' } = Astro.props;
const siteName = 'Baby Skin Lab';
const fullTitle = title === siteName ? title : `${title} — ${siteName}`;
const url = new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site).toString();
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>{fullTitle}</title>
<meta name="description" content={description} />
<link rel="canonical" href={url} />
<meta property="og:type" content={ogType} />
<meta property="og:site_name" content={siteName} />
<meta property="og:title" content={fullTitle} />
<meta property="og:description" content={description} />
<meta property="og:url" content={url} />
<meta property="og:locale" content="ko_KR" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable.css" />
<slot name="head" />
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="wrap">
    <a class="logo" href="/">Baby Skin Lab<span class="dot">.</span></a>
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/tools/아기-피부-증상-진단기/">증상 진단기</a>
      <a href="/guides/">가이드</a>
      <a href="/about/">소개</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>
<main>
  <slot />
</main>
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p><strong>Baby Skin Lab</strong> — 아기 피부 상태를 판정하고 케어 방향을 제시하는 도구 랩</p>
    <p>운영: 주식회사 빌리지베이비 (러베 ruuve 운영사) · 본 사이트의 판정 결과는 참고용이며 의학적 진단이 아닙니다. 증상이 지속되면 소아청소년과 진료를 받아주세요.</p>
    <p><a href="/about/">사이트 소개</a> · <a href="/disclaimer/">의료 면책</a></p>
  </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
